Obulwadde bwa T obwa T obwa T obuyitibwa T lymphocyte bulina obubonero bwa CD4+CD8+T era bulina obuvunaanyizibwa bwa maanyi mu bulwadde bwa T.
CD4+T cells zireetera B cells okukola antibodies ez'enjawulo ku virus, ate CD8+T cells zitta obutundu obuli mu virus.
Obusimu bw'ebisenge bya T bwongera okuleeta obutwa obuyitibwa cytokines obuyitibwa pre-inflammatory, nga bw'obuyamba obutasobola kuddamu kusanyalala.
