Kyokka, abalwadde 80 ku buli 100 beetaaga obuyambi bw'okufuuyira, omuwendo ogusinga ogw'abo abalina COVID-19, era nga gukwatagana n'omuwendo gw'abantu abafa MERS okusinga aba COVID-19.
Obulwadde bwa ssennyiga (26%) n'okwokya mu nsingo (21%) nabyo byalabikira mu balwadde ba MERS.
Mu balwadde ba SARS, okusaasaana (100%-99%), ekikulukuto ekikalu (75%-29%), okusannyalala (42%-40%), okusaanuuka (25%-20), n'okwokya mu kamwa (25%-13) bye byali ebirwadde ebikulu era nga 20%-14% ku abo abaalina akawuka ako beetaaga okuyambibwa.
Omwagalwa wa COVID-19 ku lunaku lwa Febwali 14, yali 2% ate nga abantu abakakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde buno mu nsi yonna baali 66,576.
