Ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu eky'ensi yonna kiwakanya COVID-19 nga kawumpuli w'ensi yonna
Ku Lwokusatu, ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu (WHO) kyayita okubaluka kw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ekireetebwa akawuka ka corona akayitibwa SARS-CoV-2 nti kifuuse kawuka ak'ensi yonna.
Wadde ng'ekigambo "obubonero" kitegeeza engeri obulwadde gye bubunyeemu, so si engeri gye buyinza okuba obw'omutawaana, WHO eraga nti gavumenti zirina okubaako kye zikola:
Akulira WHO, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, agambye nti ensi zonna zisobola okukyusa enkola y'ekirwadde kino.
Singa ensi zifuna abantu abaagalwa, ne zibatunula, ne babawa obujjanjabi, ne babanoonya, bandibadde bawulira bulungi.
Tulinayo okweraliikirira okw'amaanyi olw'omuwendo gw'abantu abafa era n'obutabanguko obuliwo.
Okusinziira ku Dr. Tom Friedan, eyaliko akulira Ekitongole ky'Amerika eky'Okukuma n'Okukugira Endwadde, ekirwadde kino "tekisobola kuvumirirwa".
"Mu biwandiiko ebifulumiziddwa CNN mu February, yagamba nti, "Okuggyako ekirwadde kya 'flu,' tewali kirwadde kya mukenenya kirala kye baanoonyerezaako okuva lwe kyabaluka okutuuka lwe kyabalukawo mu nsi yonna".
Gebbryus naye yayogerera ku nsonga y'emu, ng'agamba nti "Tulina kawumpuli yenna eyava ku ssenyiga wa Corona".
Era yagattako nti, "Era tetulabangawo kawumpuli akyasobola okufugibwa mu kiseera kye kimu".
Ekisaakaate kino ekippya ky'ekikungo ky'ensi yonna ky'ava ku kusalawo kwa WHO mu Jjanwali okulangirira nti embeera eno ey'akabenje mu nsi yonna erina okukolebwa mu nsi yonna.
Omukulu w'ekitongole ky'Amerika ekirwanyisa endwadde eziruma, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yayogera ku kawuka kano nti: "Mu bbanga ttono, kigenda kikendeera".
Omwa Kihosi, Associated Press erikanganaya ngoku hakuli obuli 126,000 ab'abandu ababya n'omubulhwere obukalire bwa COVID-19 omwa kihugho, kandi ibalhabire omwa bandi ab'ebihumbi 4600.
Olutalo lwa coronavirus olwa 2019-20 bwe bulwadde obuva ku coronavirus (COVID-19) obuva ku kirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2 ekiyitibwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okulukawo kuno kwazuulibwa mu Wuhan, China mu December wa 2019, kwalangirirwa nga Public Health Emergency of International Concern mu January 30, 2020, era ne kuyitibwa Global Pandemic mu March 11, 2020.
Nga 10 Apuli 2020, abantu obukadde 1.61 beebalina COVID-19 mu nsi 210 n'ebitundu, era abantu nga 97,000 be baafa.
Abantu 364,000 beebakawona.
Omuwendo gw'abafa gubalibwa okuba 4% mu China, ate mu nsi yonna guli wakati wa 13.04% mu Algeria ne 0.08% mu New Zealand.
Obubonero obutera okulabika butwaliramu okukomba, okukaaba, n'okufuna obuzibu bw'okubuuka.
Obuzibu obuva ku mbeera eno buyinza okuzingiramu obuwuka bw'omu byenda n'obubonero obuva ku mbeera y'obutereevu bw'omukka.
Obulwadde buno busobola okubalukawo mu nnaku nga ttaano, naye busobola okubalukawo mu nnaku ebbiri oba 14.
Tewali ddagala lya kawuka erimanyiddwa oba eddagala ly'okuggya akawuka kano.
Obujjanjabi obusookerwako bubeera obujjanjabi obujjanjabisa obujjanjabisa. Obujjanjabi obujjanjabwa mu kulwanyisa obulwadde buno buzingiramu okunaaba engalo, okwambala ekyuma ekikka ku mimwa ng'okozesa kkoyino, okwekweka wala okuva ku bantu abalala, n'okwekweka n'okwekutula ku bantu abalala singa omuntu oyo ateeberezebwa okuba n'obulwadde.
Ab'obuyinza okwetooloola ensi yonna bazzeemu nga batandika okuteekawo obukwakkulizo bw'entambula, okussa abantu mu buwambe, okuyimiriza entambula, okufuga obuzibu bw'obutonde, n'okuggalawo ebizimbe.
