Ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) kyalabye enjawulo wakati w'obulwadde bwa SARS mu 2002-2004. Gavumenti ya Sin yagambibwa okuba n'ekyama ku bulwadde buno, ekyaleetawo obuzibu mu kugezaako okuziyiza obulwadde buno n'obutabulirawo, nga Gavumenti eya Uganda "ewadde amateeka ag'okugema okusaasaana mu bifo by'ekyeya mu New York City".
Nga 23/1/20, nga addamu ku kusalawo kwa gavumenti eya wakati okuziyiza okuyingira mu kibuga Wan, omubaka wa WHO Gaudin Gaulya yagamba nti wadde "teyali mu buyinza bwa WHO" kyali "kabonero akakulu ak'okuziyiza ekirwadde okusaasaana mu kitundu ekirwadde we kyali kisinga okuba eky'amaanyi". Era yabayita "ekyafaayo eky'obulamu obwa bulijjo". Nga 30/1/20, ekirwadde kino kyasaasaana okuva ku muntu okudda ku muntu mu nsi endala era n'omuwendo gw'abalwadde gweyongedde mu nsi endala.
Omukulembeze w'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte Tedros Adhanom yagamba nti ekiddako okulangirirwa kw'embeera ey'obulabe mu nsi yonna "kwali okutya nti obulwadde buno buyinza okusaasaana mu nsi yonna, naddala mu mawanga amavu era agatali mu by'enfuna nga tegalina nkola ya bujjanjabi ya maanyi".
Mu kwanukula ku bikwata ku kutandikawo okuwerebwa kw'entambula, Tedros yagamba nti "tewali nsonga yonna ey'okwenyigira mu bikolwa eby'obutaba na bwenkanya mu by'entambula n'obusuubuzi mu nsi yonna" era nti "ensi yonna tejja kukkiriza mateeka gakugira eby'obusuubuzi n'ebyenfuna".
Ku 5/2, Ekitongole ky'Eby'Obulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) kyalagira ensi yonna okugaba obukadde bwa ddoola 675 ez'okuyamba amawanga agali mu bwetaavu, nga kibakubiriza okuwagira amawanga "agalina enkola ey'okwekebejja abantu abalina akawuka ka siriimu, ne bwe kaba mu mbeera enzibu ennyo".
Tedros yayongedde okunnyonnyola nti "okutuuka ku buwanguzi kitwetaagisa ffenna okufuba", era n'akubiriza amawanga gonna "okuwaayo leero oba oluvanyuma" nga 11/2, ekibiina ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu bwe kyawa empapula z'amawulire COVID-19 ng'erinnya ly'obulwadde.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu, Tedros yategeeza nti Ssaabawandiisi w'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte Antonio Guterres yakkirizza "okuteeka mu nkola amaanyi gonna ag'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte".
Omukulembeze w'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte mu katyabaga yayimbulwa ng'ekyavaamu, ekyaleetera ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte okwongera amaanyi mu kukola ku bulwadde, nga kino kyasobozesa ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna "okukuumira ebirowoozo ku bujjanjabi ng'ate abalala basobola okuleeta obumanyirivu mu kukuuma enkolagana mu bantu, mu by'enfuna, n'okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kw'obulwadde. "
Ku 14/2, akulira ekitongole kya WHO eky'okuteeka mu nkola enteekateeka ya SEN yakwatibwa okuwaayo abakugu okuva mu nsi yonna n'ekitongole kya WHO eri ensi ya SEN okuyamba mu kutegeka n'okulabirira mu nsi yonna "amaanyi n'obuyinza bw'obulwadde", okutegeka ebivuganyo n'okukuŋŋaana awamu n'ekitongole ekikulu ku mutindo gw'eggwanga n'okufuga entambula y'ekitundu okusalawo ku "kikozesebwa mu nsi yonna okw'abantu ababeera mu bitundu eby'ewala n'ebitundu ebirala, nga mw'otwalidde n'obutonde bw'ebibuga n'eby'ebitundu by'eŋŋanda". Ku 25/2, WHO yagamba nti "ensi yonna erina okwongera okwetegekera ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe", era n'egamba nti wadde nga kyali kitandise, amawanga galina "okubeera abeetegefu".
Mu kwebuuza ku kulwala okwekulaakulanya mu Iran, ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) kyasindika ekibinja mu Iran okwetegereza embeera. Nga 28, WHO yategeeza mu butongole nti okutya kwa coronavirus okw'ensi yonna kulinnya okuva ku "kulina" okutuuka ku "kulina", nga kino kye kibinja ekisinga okuba eky'obulabe n'obweraliikirivu.
Mike Ryan, akulira enteekateeka z'eddembe mu kitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna ekya WHO, yategeezezza ensi yonna mu kiwandiiko nti "Waliwo ekigezo ekikulu eri gavumenti zonna ku nsi: Okuzuukuka".
Obulwadde busobola okuba nga bujja era balina okwetegekera, "Okumanya engeri entuufu ey'okuddamu kuyinza okuyamba ensi yonna okwewala ekisinga okuba ekibi".
RIA yategeezezza nti ekirwadde kino tekirina kigendererwa kya kulangirira bulwadde bwa nsi yonna, n'agamba nti okulangirira kuno kitegeeza nti "tukkiriza nti buli muntu ku nsi alina akabi akali mu kirwadde kino".
Nga 11 March, ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu (WHO) kyalaga nti ekirwadde kya ssennyiga omukambwe kya ssennyiga wa corona.
Omukulu w'ekitongole ky'eby'obulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) yagamba nti "ekikungo kino kivudde ku kuba nti ekikungo kino kiyongedde okugaziwa, era nga kivudde ku kuba nti kiva ku kuba nti kitambula mpolampola". WHO yavumirira nnyo nnyo ekitundu ekitalabika eky'ekikangabwa kino, omwali okulangirira nti ekirwadde kino kizibu nnyo eri abantu bonna, n'okukitwala nga kawumpuli.
Okubuusabuusa kwa bantu kwazingiramu okusaba kw'akulira ekibiina ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna, Tedros Adhamon, okuyimirirwa, okwasiddwa emikono 733,000 mu 6/4.
Nga 26/3, akakiiko k'abakugu mu ddembe ly'obuntu mu nsi yonna ak'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte kaakakasa nti eddembe ly'obuntu lyeyongera okussibwamu ekitiibwa mu kiseera ky'ekirwadde kya COVID-19.
Ekibiina kino kigamba nti buli muntu alina okuteekebwa mu bulamu obweyagaza era nti gavumenti y'erina obuvunaanyizibwa.
Ekibinja ky'abantu kino kikiggumiza nti ebbula ly'ebikozesebwa oba obujjanjabi tebirina kubaawo ng'ensonga ey'okusosola abantu mu bibiina ebimu.
Abakugu baakakasa nti buli muntu alina eddembe mu mbeera y'obulamu, omuli abantu abatalina busobozi, abantu abava mu mawanga amalala, bannamukadde, ab'oludda oluvugibwa mu ggwanga, abantu abatalina maka, abo abali mu buzibu, abasibe, abantu abeenoonyeza obubudamu, n'abantu abalala abatalina buyambi bwa gavumenti.
Enkola z'eggwanga z'ebyenfuna n'abantu mu kiseera kya COVID-19 zireeseewo obuzibu mu nsi yonna.
Ekibiina ky'ensi yonna ekikola ku by'enfuna n'enkulaakulana (OECD) kitongozza omukutu ogutegekeddwa okuwa abantu amagezi ku ngeri y'okuddamu mu nsonga z'eby'obufuzi mu nsi yonna, n'okukubaganya ebirowoozo ku nsonga ezo.
Okuva ku poliisi n'ebikozesebwa mu by'obulamu n'eby'enfuna mu nsi yonna okulaga engeri ebiragiro ku kutambuza abantu gye bikosaamu, omutwe gw'empuliziganya gw'egatta ku pulaani y'eggwanga, n'ebiruubirirwa ebigenderako okuyamba ensi okuyiga okuva mu nkola ya buli emu n'okusobozesa ensi yonna okukolaganira awamu okulwanyisa ssenyiga omukambwe.
Gavumenti ya Sin yakopeddwa ab'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte ne minisita wa Bungereza mu kabineti ya Michael Gove ne mutabani wa Pulezidenti wa Brazil Eduardo Bolsonaro olw'engeri embi gye bakuumiddemu ekirwadde kino, ekyatandikira mu kibuga Sin mu ssaza ly'e Hubei.
Abakulembeze b'ebibiina mu bitundu bya Sin beewogoma ku kaweefube w'okusaanyawo ekitundu kya Sin, akabonero akalaga nti ebibiina by'obufuzi tebyafaayo ku ngeri ebibiina by'obufuzi gye biyinza okubuuliramu mu kitundu ekyo.
Abamu ku bannamawulire bagamba nti kino kyakolebwa okukuuma Ssekyankalya w'ekibiina kya Sin Ki-moon, Shin Ki-moon, okuva ku njala mu kiseera kya ssenyiga omukambwe.
Abakungu abamu, gamba nga Juan Lizan, baagaana okukkiriza nti Coronavirus yava mu kibuga Wan, ne bawagira enteekateeka z'obuyambi bwa COVID-19 mu Amerika oba mu Yitale.
Pulezidenti Donald Trump ayise ekirwadde kino "Sini Virus" oba "Virusi emu" era n'agamba nti abakuumi ba Sini bakungudde ekirwadde kino ekirwadde ekikyasinze okusaasaana mu nsi yonna. Kino kyayisiddwa mu kusooka abavumirizi abangi nga ky'obusosoze n'okusaasira olw'okulemererwa kwa Pulezidenti okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino.
Daily Beast yafuna amawulire nti omu ku ba UN agenda kukola endagaano y'okutambula n'omubaka wa National Security Council, era nti enteekateeka eno yalimu ebigambo ebitegeeza nti "Byonna bikwata ku Bba".
Twagambibwa nti tugezaako okusaasaanya obubaka buno mu ngeri yonna, mu lukungaana lw'amawulire ne mu kulabikako ku ttivvi, ebikozesebwa nga bannabyabufuzi, poliisi y'ebweru w'eggwanga ne Bloomberg baategeezezza nti okufuba kwa China okuyamba ensi eziriko akawuka kano ngeri ya ppokopoko.
Akulira poliisi y'ebweru wa Bulaaya, Joseph Borel, alabudde nti ekizibu ky'obupuliiki obuli mu nsi kiva ku buzibu obuliwo mu nsi yonna, nga mw'otwalidde n'ebyobulamu n'obutebenkevu.
Borrell era yagambye nti "Sina y'ensibuko y'obubaka bw'amaanyi nti, okwawukana ku United Nations, ye munnaffe omukuumi era omwesigika".
Ssenno era yeeyita UN okuggyawo ebibonerezo ku Syria, Venezuela ne Iran, abagamba nti baateranga okugaba obuyambi mu nsi ezo.
Jack Ma kye yawaayo okuwagira Cuba, nga kuliko amasimu 100,000, kyaggyibwa mu bbanka ya UN ku lunaku lwa 3/4.
Ate era, ekibiina ky'Amawanga Amagatte kyayimbulwa nti kyabuusizza amawanga amalala agaali gaagala okubawa obuyambi.
Ate era, waliwo endagaano ezikwata ku kutuma masiki wakati w'amawanga agamu, gamba nga Germany, Austria ne Switzerland, Czech Republic ne Italy.
Ng'oggyeko ekyo, Turkey yawamba ebyuma by'empuliziganya eby'omulembe ebikumi bisatu ebyali bigendereddwa okugabibwa mu Spain.
Ku ntandikwa ya March, gavumenti ya Italy yanenya obuyambi obutonotono obuva mu EU mu bakwatibwa obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe mu Italy.
Maurizio Massari, omubaka wa Italy mu EU, yagamba nti "Kye kyakolebwa Siini kyali kya buwagizi bwokka".
Kya lwatu, kino tekiraga nti abantu ba Yakuwa bawagira gavumenti ya Bulaaya.
Ku 22/3/2017, oluvannyuma lw'okukuba essimu ne Katikkiro wa Yitale Giuseppe Conte, Pulezidenti wa Russia Vladimir Putin yakubiriza amagye g'omu Russia okusindika abaserikale, mmotoka ez'enjawulo ez'okusaanyaawo obuwuka, n'ebintu ebirala eby'obujjanjabi mu Yitale.
Omuwandiisi w'amawulire Omutalyani La Stampa yafuna obujulizi okuva mu bifo eby'enjawulo eby'eby'obufuzi nti obuyambi obwali buweebwa Russia mu myaka 80 egy'obukulu tebwali bwa mugaso oba nga tebwamu kalungi konna eri Italy.
Ensonda zikoowedde nti Russia erina obuzibu mu by'obufuzi ne by'obwannakyewa era nti erumbye abavuganya.
Pulezidenti wa Lombard, Atilio Fontana, ne Minisita w'ensonga z'ebweru w'e Italy, Luigi Di Maio, baabuusizza ebivudde mu mawulire era ne bategeeza nti basiimye nnyo.
Russia era yasindika ebyuma ebirimu eddagala eri Amerika.
Omwogezi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagamba nti "Bwe baba basindika obuyambi eri UN, Putin agamba nti bwe wabaawo obuyambi obujja okuva mu UN, ebyuma by'eddwaliro n'ebintu bye bijja okuggibwa mu bbaasi, bajja kuba beetegefu okubikyusa singa kiba kyetaagisa".
Omukolo gw'amagye g'omu mwaka gwa 2020 mu Bugirimaani, Poland, n'amawanga ga Baltic, gwe gwasinga obunene mu by'okulwanyisa amagye okuva ku kiseera ky'olutalo olutabukidde.
Kampeyini y'amagye eya General Kate Hudson yanenya entekateeka y'eby'obuvuzi eya 2020 ng'agamba nti, "Mu kiseera kino eky'obuzibu bw'eby'obulamu, kino kitadde obulamu bw'abantu mu katyabaga, si ku magye g'amawanga amagatte ga United Nations gokka n'ag'amawanga ga Bulaaya gonna, naye n'abantu mu nsi ezikola emirimu egitali gya busamize". Gavumenti ya Iran yakwatibwa nnyo akawuka, nga mu bano mulimu ababaka ba palamenti babiri n'abantu 15 abaliko kati n'abava dda.
Katikkiro wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yawandiika ebbaluwa eri abakulembeze b'ensi yonna nga 14/3/2020 ng'asaba obuyambi, ng'agamba nti eggwanga lye lirina obuzibu olw'obulwadde obuli mu nsi yonna olw'obutaba na nkolagana n'amasoko g'ensi yonna ng'ekivuddeko okubonerezebwa kw'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte ku Iran, obulwadde buno bwe bwaleetera ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte okujja mu maaso n'okutuusa obuyambi ku bantu mu nsi ezaakula eddagala, omuli obujjanjabi bw'ensi yonna, obujjanjabi bw'abaana, ebibiina ebiyamba amaka, n'okugaba obuyambi ku by'obulamu mu nsi yonna.
Abakugu mu by'obufuzi baategeezezza nti kino kiyinza okubaako kye kikola ku ssuubi lya Trump ery'okuddamu okulondebwa mu kalulu k'obwapulezidenti aka 2020. Enkolagana y'obuweereza wakati wa Japan ne South Korea ye yaleetera ekirwadde kino okusaasaana.
South Korea yanenya "obunnanfuusi n'obuteegendereza" bwa Japan. Japan bwe yalangirira nti omuntu yenna eyava South Korea alina okweyawula mu bifo bya gavumenti eby'enjawulo okumala wiiki bbiri.
Abantu mu South Korea baayawukana ku ngeri Moon Jae-in gye yayanukulamu ku kizibu kino.
Abatuuze bangi mu Korea beemulugunya nti oba balina okuvunaana Moon mu kkooti olw'engeri embi gye baatwalamu ekirwadde kino. Ekizibu kino kiwadde amawanga omukisa okuyisa amateeka mu mbeera ey'obudde.
Abamu bagamba nti kino kisobozesa gavumenti okwongera amaanyi mu bufuzi.
Mu Hungary, palamenti yavuganya okuleka Ssaabaminisita Viktor Orbán okuyisa ebiragiro, era n'okugoba palamenti n'okulonda n'okusala emisango ku abo abaaba babuuzizza amawulire agatali matuufu ku kawuka ka HIV n'engeri gavumenti gy'eyisizzaamu mu kizibu kino.
