Okubeerawo kwa fayiro mu bifaananyi kwazuulibwa mu RT-PCR ekola ku RNA ya coronavirus.
Okunoonyereza kuno kwa njawulo era kwategekebwa okunoonyereza ku RNA eya SARS-CoV-2 yokka.
Kino kiyamba mu kukwata obulwadde obupya ennyo era obuliko obuwuka obuyitirira.
Okunoonyereza ku nsolo z'omu mubiri kuyinza okukozesebwa mu kukebera endwadde n'okujjanjaba abantu.
