Okukebera ku bifa ku polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) kuyinza okukolebwa ku bifa ku by'okussa ebiwundu ebifunibwa okuva mu bika bya siriimu, omuli okukebera ku kamwa, olubu n'ebiva mu kusika.
